description:
Sit down with us as Napoleon, Town, and Eric chop it up with Steph, the co-founder of Young King Haircare.

We touch on Ice Cubes interaction in the presidents campaign, voting in 2020, starting a business as an entrepreneur, and his families product line, Young King Haircare.
